snippet.title: Attack of the Karens | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The Karens Invade in 2022.  Are you ready? 


Attack of the Karens is a 2D side-scrolling bullet hell shoot 'em up where you have to fight to save your city from spoiled, entitled cyborg women and their robot army! 



Steam: 


https://store.steampowered.com/app/1566670?utm_source=ytteaser


https://www.studioprimitive.net
